<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" /><meta name="description" content="ATProto OAuth authorization page" />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <link rel="preload" href="/s/login.css" as="style" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/s/login.css" /><style></style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div id="root">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:flex md:flex-row md:justify-stretch md:items-center min-h-screen min-w-screen bg-white text-slate-900 dark:bg-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">
        <div class="px-6 pt-4 w-full md:max-w-lg flex flex-row md:flex-col md:self-stretch md:w-1/2 md:max-w-fix md:p-4 md:text-right md:dark:border-r md:dark:border-slate-700 md:bg-slate-100 md:dark:bg-slate-800">
        <div class="flex-grow grid content-center md:justify-items-end">
          <h1 class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-5xl md:my-4 font-semibold text-brand">Identify</h1>
          <p class="hidden md:block max-w-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Enter your <b class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Bluesky (ATProto)</b> handle</p></div>
          
          </div>
          <main class="w-full p-6 md:max-w-3xl md:px-12">
            <form method="post" class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <p><span><b class="">{{host}}</b><span class="opacity-50">/client-metadata.json</span></span> is asking for your handle on the Bluesky (ATProto) network.</p>
                <p>By clicking <b>Identify</b> you allow this application to redirect you to the authorization page of the server that hosts your Bluesky (ATProto) data.</p>
                {{#if error}}
                <p class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">{{error}}</p>
                {{/if}}
              <p>
                <label for="handle" class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200" style="margin-right: 30px"><b>Handle</b></label>
                <b class="accent-slate-100 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-500 dark:text-slate-300 border-solid border-2 border-transparent focus:border-brand focus:bg-slate-200 has-[:focus]:bg-slate-200 dark:focus:bg-slate-700 dark:has-[:focus]:bg-slate-700 rounded-lg py-1 px-2 m-1 md:m-2" style="margin-right:-25px; padding:5px 15px 5px 5px;">@</b>
                <input type="text" name="handle" id="handle" class="w-60 accent-slate-100 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 border-solid border-2 border-transparent focus:border-brand focus:bg-slate-200 has-[:focus]:bg-slate-200 dark:focus:bg-slate-700 dark:has-[:focus]:bg-slate-700 rounded-lg py-1 px-2 m-1 md:m-2" placeholder="{{default handle "username.bsky.social"}}" aria-label="Handle" required />
              </p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap flex-row-reverse items-center justify-end space-x-reverse space-x-2">
                <button role="Button" type="submit" class="rounded-lg truncate cursor-pointer touch-manipulation tracking-wide overflow-hidden py-2 px-6 accent-slate-100 bg-brand text-brand-c disabled:opacity-50">Identify</button>
                <button role="Button" type="button" onclick="history.back()" class="rounded-lg truncate cursor-pointer touch-manipulation tracking-wide overflow-hidden py-2 px-6 accent-brand text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 disabled:opacity-50">Deny id</button>
                <div class="flex-auto"></div>
              </div>
              </form>
              </main>
              </div>
              </div>


    <div id="root"></div>
    </body>
</html>